咩可以拯救番佢地? ☁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n舊機已經唔係手？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲係度呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec5d0a545046b8339bbe49f3b4a78f6929f3d553","tid":414923,"uid":32577,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:07:47.000Z","msg":"成就未解鎖"},{"pid":"81223f9da1b36a50a8daff89cd52c6da35fb3e0d","tid":414923,"uid":19517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:10:54.000Z","msg":"慘得過我 相機壞左backup晒 整完Restore話備份損毀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc7e169726d81936e8eddcd681c3054b693be46","tid":414923,"uid":6953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:11:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>嗯 明白 咁兩位請問我有無啲咩可以拯救番佢地? ☁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n舊機已經唔係手？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲係度呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你係舊機開返whatsapp . setting, chat backup, 做多次backup, 新機del 個whatsapp 佢，再download 過 whatsapp,佢會問你 re 唔recovery, 你recovery 多次就得<br />\n<br />\n不過你咁做 你新機呢幾日嘅對話會無咗。變返舊機嘅對話"},{"pid":"973ac9729aef5a34f26a8d800cdc311e3400eb6b","tid":414923,"uid":6953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:12:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慘得過我 相機壞左backup晒 整完Restore話備份損毀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nicloud 定 itunes?"},{"pid":"e974f39e763b871309c1e9b0038a1405c2321c69","tid":414923,"uid":6953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:15:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>嗯 明白 咁兩位請問我有無啲咩可以拯救番佢地? ☁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n舊機已經唔係手？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲係度呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你係舊機開返whatsapp . setting, chat backup, 做多次backup, 新機del 個whatsapp 佢，再download 過 whatsapp,佢會問你 re 唔recovery, 你recovery 多次就得<br />\n<br />\n不過你咁做 你新機呢幾日嘅對話會無咗。變返舊機嘅對話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要同一個icloud id <br />\n今次你對清楚icloud storage 夠唔夠whatsapp backup<br />\n<br />\n有時whatsapp 個server 如果食rr到你個backup ,你可能要delete 舊嘅icloud 上嘅backup, 由頭backup 多次<br />\n<br />\n(其實你每次backup whatsapp, icloud 唔會重覆backuk 你舊資料，只會backup 新add 嘅野。如果你本身whatsapp 上backup server 有問題，你唔del 舊backup 就再backup,係解決唔到）"},{"pid":"2117fb4953ec8a569c64acc61d097a85b9f2c30c","tid":414923,"uid":2950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:22:35.000Z","msg":"最好係itunes同icloud各一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8eefacc057bdb2243e6b7469c7f2f6e8bd5f0a7","tid":414923,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:49:42.000Z","msg":"佢舊機係咪android?<br />\n你係咪用果個software 去 transfer?<br />\n<br />\n如果係IOS<br />\n你產左舊既iCloud 上backup<br />\n重新build過一份backup就應該咩都sync 到"},{"pid":"abf58c805310dec0f25aefff7b07363d5ab5c150","tid":414923,"uid":38625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:51:35.000Z","msg":"前幾日好似壞wts 死晒圖和對話<br />\n如果backup左 都開唔返<br />\n你預無硬"},{"pid":"49207923f3136295fada6e3d635cf058163f83d6","tid":414923,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:32:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e33b62c13104911cf425f621862fc5d453167fb","tid":414923,"uid":82955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:04:18.000Z","msg":"用左舊機重新再backup果個方法<br />\n成 功 左 啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img